iv class="t m0 x22 h4 y17e ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">因此，<span class="_ _9"></span>发展的话，<span class="_ _6"></span>要内、外一起发展；<span class="_ _6"></span>幸福的话，<span class="_ _9"></span>要考</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y17f ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">虑今生、<span class="_ _17"></span>来世的幸福；<span class="_ _17"></span>教育的话，<span class="_ _12"></span>要兼顾德、<span class="_ _17"></span>才二者。<span class="_ _17"></span>当然，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y26 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">这方面有很多内容可谈，<span class="_ _8"></span>我今天只是抛砖引玉，<span class="_ _8"></span>象征性地简</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y27 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">单提一下。大家若想深入了解，可以学习佛教的诸多经论，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y28 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">从中你定会发现具有价值的“珍宝”<span class="_ _7"></span>。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
